title: RHOBH: Sisters Are Ruinin' It For Themselves
description:
It's the moment we've been waiting all year for: Kathy vs. Rinna in part three of the Real Housewives of Beverly Hills reunion. We learned so many things: Rinna was abused in the dark, Kathy may have said the F-word, and Erika is getting some D. But if there's one thing to take away from this season, it's that IT'S ALL KYLE'S FAULT, GUYZZZAH!

Watch our recap with Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/73859876?pr=true
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
